        <name xml:lang="en">transport, freight train</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">metric ton*km</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. Weighted average distance to Coya Sur (where the product is further processed)  from two mining location, by production volume: Pampa Blanca 375,000 t and 90 km and Nueva Victoria 1,000,000 t and 185 km. Train transport was considered as main transport based on "sodium nitrate production, unrefined from caliche ore mining, CL". Volumes taken from 
Ordóñez, J. et al. (2017) “Heap Leaching of Caliche Ore. Modeling of a Multicomponent System with Particle Size Distribution” https://doi.org/10.3390/min7100180.</comment>
